==English==
===Verb===
'''to turbocharge'''
# to [[increase]] the [[power]] of an [[internal combustion engine]] (either [[Otto]] or [[Diesel]] [[cycle]]) by [[compressing]] the [[inlet]] air with [[power]] extracted from the [[exhaust]] air.
# to make faster, more powerful.

